### Create successful mock payment
POST http://localhost:8083/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "{{bookingId}}",
  "userId": "user-1",
  "amount": 1500.00,
  "currency": "INR",
  "paymentMethodToken": "pm_success"
}

### Create declined mock payment
POST http://localhost:8083/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "{{bookingId}}",
  "userId": "user-1",
  "amount": 1500.00,
  "currency": "INR",
  "paymentMethodToken": "pm_card_declined"
}

### Simulate payment provider timeout
POST http://localhost:8083/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "{{bookingId}}",
  "userId": "user-1",
  "amount": 1500.00,
  "currency": "INR",
  "paymentMethodToken": "pm_timeout"
}

### Get one payment
GET http://localhost:8083/api/payments/{{paymentId}}

### Get payments for booking
GET http://localhost:8083/api/payments?bookingId={{bookingId}}

### Get payments for user
GET http://localhost:8083/api/payments?userId=user-1

### Refund succeeded payment
PATCH http://localhost:8083/api/payments/{{paymentId}}/refund
